rcourt lists}}\n{{Port Harcourt}}\n\n[[Category:Hospitals in Port Harcourt|*]]\n[[Category:Port Harcourt-related lists|Hospitals]]\n[[Category:Lists of hospitals by city|Port Harcourt]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{Use Nigerian English|date=October 2019}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2017}}\nList of some [[hospitals]] and [[Medical facility|medical centers]] in the city of [[Port Harcourt]] , [[Nigeria]].\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Name !! Location\n|-\n| [[Meridian Hospitals]] || [[21 Igbokwe Street, Port Harcourt|D-Line]]\n|-\n| Atinu Critical Care Hospital || [[Elelenwo, Port Harcourt|Elelenwo]]\n|-\n| [[Braithwaite Memorial Specialist Hospital]] || [[Old GRA, Port Harcourt|Old GRA]]<ref name=\"hos1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.bmsh.org.ng/ |title=Braithwaite Memorial Hospital |publisher=bmsh.org.ng |date= |accessdate=2014-06-10 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140816200151/http://www.bmsh.org.ng/ |archivedate=2014-08-16 |df= }}</ref>\n|-\n| Calvary Hospital || Orazi\n|-\n| C.Bennett Specialist Hospital || Ada-George Road, \nBy Open Doors\n|-\n| Chris The King Hospital|| [[Oyigbo]] \n|-\n| Cova Care Specialist Hospital and Endoscopy Centre || Eliozu\n|-\n| Daily Spring Hospital || [[Old GRA, Port Harcourt|Old GRA]]\n|-\n| [[Rivers State Dental and Maxillofacial Hospital|Dental and Maxillofacial Hospital]] || Garrison<ref name=\"tide newspaper1\">{{cite news|url=http://www.thetidenewsonline.com/2013/02/04/%E2%80%98ph-new-hub-for-medical-tourism%E2%80%99/|title=PH, New Hub For Medical Tourism|last=|first=|date=2013-02-04|work=[[The Tide (Nigeria)|The Tide]]|location=[[Port Harcourt]], [[Nigeria]]|publisher=Rivers State Newspaper Corporation|accessdate=2014-06-11}}</ref>\n|-\n| Destiny Hospital || [[Diobu, Port Harcourt|Diobu]]\n|-\n| El-Bene Hospital || [[D-line, Port Harcourt|D-line]]\n|-\n| El-Specialist Hospital || [[D-line, Port Harcourt|D-line]]\n|-\n| First Rivers Hospital || Rumuomasi\n|-\